---
const traps = [
  'Maximize your returns',
  'Minimize your taxes',
  'Get the most house you can afford',
  'Squeeze every dollar',
];
---

<section class="py-24 md:py-36 bg-warm-stone grain-overlay">
  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <!-- Section header: left-aligned editorial -->
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <p class="text-storehouse-400 font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase reveal">
        The problem
      </p>
      <h2 class="mt-4 font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-warm-white leading-[1.05] reveal reveal-delay-1">
        We've been taught to<br />
        <em class="not-italic text-storehouse-400">maximize everything.</em>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Content grid -->
    <div class="mt-16 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-8">
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <p class="text-lg text-warm-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          Modern financial advice is obsessed with optimization:
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4">
          {traps.map((trap) => (
            <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-storehouse-400 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <span class="text-lg text-warm-white/80">{trap}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-6 lg:col-start-7 reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-warm-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            The result? Lives filled to the edges. No room for surprise. No space for generosity. No margin for the unexpected.
          </p>
          <p class="text-warm-white font-medium text-xl">
            This is the optimization trap.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Transition quote -->
    <div class="mt-20 reveal">
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-px bg-warm-white/20"></div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-10 font-quote text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-warm-white/80 text-center italic leading-snug max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        "Storehouse is built on a different premise."
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
